.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be used in the same context with</tr_>, c. dat., <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.706</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ συμφραζόμενα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the context</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.22a</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.707</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18(1).437</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n98937.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be synonymous with</tr_>, c. dat., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0719.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aret.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ SD\">SD</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.5</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}